    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>A Grave-Wisp is a small, flickering spirit of cold light that drifts through darkness. It appears as a distant campfire, a familiar face, or a beckoning lantern—luring the living into the frozen embrace of the Frost-Draugr it serves.</p>",
      "director": "<p>Wisps exist to pin targets in place for the Draugr. Lure pulls PCs into Cold Aura range; Cold Touch locks them there. Kill the wisps first or suffer the Draugr's patient, crushing advance.</p>",
